videos.description: After the Lakers' Game 3 victory over the Rockets, LeBron James explains how the team is using the memory of Kobe Bryant to fuel their playoff run.

videos.headline: LeBron: Lakers hope to make Kobe proud

videos.description: Anthony Davis heaps praise on teammate LeBron James following the Lakers' Game 3 win, saying it feels like the 35-year-old is "drinking from the fountain of youth."
